result.name: De Luna Tapas Bar &Restaurant

reviews.text: Cocktails are amazing. Bartenders are very nice and friendly. Would recommend you to go during weekdays so you can chat with bartenders and they might serve you cocktails upon your taste. Wonderful bar in town!

Do NOT get their shisha, you will have your worse experience. You can compare it with your home boiling water steam. And when you ask them what they can do about it,  they said, no you cant do anything unless you add money......
Cocktail are not bad.
Great for the beer, also Shisha! But not for the food. Just keep drinking!
Friendly staff, great cocktails and drinks.
Wonderful service. Great bartenders. Drinks with a difference.
